Follow [INSTRUCTIONS.md](../../INSTRUCTIONS.md) for every task in this repository.

## Requirements

- **README**: Keep [README.md](../../README.md) in sync with code in the same change when you touch API endpoints, deployment/Makefile flow, database schema, local dev, or project layout (see INSTRUCTIONS.md for section mapping).
- **Frontend PRs**: Changes under `frontend/` require desktop (~1280px) and mobile (~390px) screenshots in the PR description; commit images under `docs/screenshots/` and reference branch raw URLs (see INSTRUCTIONS.md).
- **PR checklist**: Before opening a PR, verify the checklist at the end of INSTRUCTIONS.md (README API/Deployment, Makefile deploy variables, examples, screenshots).

## Do not

- Merge API or deploy work with a stale README.
- Open frontend PRs without screenshots when UI changed.
- Include changes to `frontend/scripts/capture-screenshots.mjs` in feature PRs.
